description.narrative:
This project will support an organizational capacity assessment and the development of an institutional improvement plan for the Quality Assurance and Accreditation Directorate (QAAD), Ministry of Higher Education, Afghanistan. 
The major objectives of the assessment are: 
1)	Assess the current organizational structure and management system(s) in achieving its goals; 
2)	Develop a realistic institutional development plan for changes or adjustments to ensure optimal organization and management to assist the QAAD in accomplishing its mission; 
3)	Support the development of a five-year strategic plan with the help of the institutional development plan
